Content:: Gregor Mühlberger (born 4 April 1994) is an Austrian cyclist, who currently rides for the UCI WorldTeam Movistar Team.[5][6] He was named in the start list for the 2016 Vuelta a España[7] and the start list for the 2017 Giro d'Italia.[8] In July 2018, he was named in the start list for the 2018 Tour de France.[9] He finished 70th representing Austria at the 2020 Summer Olympics in the Men's individual road race[10]
